reviewText: This DVD was awesome.. Even though it was short when it was getting really good. I would recommend this dvd
As usual Juanita Bynum preached an ON TIME WORD!!!!  Not sure when she preached this message, but it was on time for me!!!!

THIS DVD WAS AWESOME, THIS WOMAN OF GOD-(REGARDLESS HOW ANYONE FEELS ABOUT HER (NEGATIVELY) THE LORD USES HER,MY PRAYER IS THAT WE STOP TALKING ABOUT PEOPLE OF GOD AND PEOPLE IN GENERAL AND JUST PRAY FOR THE THEM.IT'S A DANGEROUS  THING PUTTING OUR MOUTH(SO TO SPEAK) ON VESSELS GOD HAS CHOSEN.,NOT TO METION IT HINDERS YOURSELF.YOU CAN'T DENY THE ANOINTING  ON DR.BYNUM LIFE.

Dr. Juanita Bynum reveals one of the powerful results of meeting God at the threshing floor in prayer - NO MORE DELAYS! What God has planned for your life will no longer be hindered or delayed as you meet Him consistently with a heart of total surrender.  If you have been encountering delays and disappointing setbacks that have threatened your purpose in God, you need to receive the impartation of NO MORE DELAYS. It will change your life.
